Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:18.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H1A1A1A&\pos(205,475)}重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:40.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H1A1A1A&\pos(665,380)}新的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以讓你一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為你和希婭一樣決定待在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你堅信對你來說這是最好的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能在理解了我的心情之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,依然不放棄 堅定向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那讓你留在我身邊也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,本來我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 現在我完全不這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再好好考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想想為什麼要跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,以後還要不要繼續待在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不得已時 我也有可能把你送回八重檻身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能用木頭造出這麼氣派的船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定沒什麼好戲看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在開派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不僅有人族 還有魔人族和亞人族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,話說這還真是燈火輝煌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嚮往和平 不畏犧牲 戰場歸來的勇者們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,非常高興我們能齊聚於此地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也很高興這場漫長的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,能以和平的形式在我這一代終止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,更高興能在一年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,親眼見證如今這如夢似幻的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.45,Default,,0,200,0,,我的內心激動不已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}難道說 這是在慶祝停戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看這情況 也只有這種可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們搞錯了梅爾基涅的主題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,原來也有過這樣的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為了結束戰爭而奔走的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,共同創造的偉業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明明並非所有隔閡都消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他們卻能如此歡笑而對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,訂立和平條約一年之後的今天 我發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這實在是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 實在是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是與野獸舉杯共飲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還是與異教徒暢談未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都是愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你們理解嗎 諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 說的就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在胡說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 諸位 如同我剛剛說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,能與諸位齊聚於此 我實在是非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是被神拋棄的邪惡種族立邦建國
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想與我們人類平起平坐的煎熬狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還是背叛唯一創世神埃希德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,崇拜無謂的異教神的愚昧之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我卻只能對他們睜一隻眼閉一隻眼的苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都將在今日終結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,除了毀滅一切 和平無處可得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為此 今日終於要一舉拿下各國首領
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在是興奮至極
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,來 神的忠實奴隸們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,揮下制裁的鐵錘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,埃希德大人 您看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來那樣就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一般來看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要往深處出發就得往船裡走的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那幅景象 說不定就是給人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,把神的瘋狂深深烙印在記憶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然後繼續探索這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是對於這個世界的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,會讓他們無法再繼續相信他們的神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛的景象 明明已經停戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然而那個像國王一樣的人卻毀約了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 稍微有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他上台的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神裡充滿著敬意與慈愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他打從心底厭惡亞人族和魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他應該不可能那麼受愛戴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只能考慮停戰之後這一年裡發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,導致了他性情大變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,反正 肯定和神脫不了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,線？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,都到這裡了還來物理陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真不要臉 這一個個解放者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 別動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,媽的煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,應該結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 所以 想讓你安慰一下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼？當然是殺了你 我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你想做的事情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,始 你為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不准用香織的聲音說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不准借香織的身體行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,盤踞在香織體內的垃圾模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道了又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個女人已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是你的女人 你要傷害她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力彈不會傷害香織的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要死的只有附身在她身上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我消失了這個女人也會壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒病吧 你不管這個女人的死活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我停止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,香織的身體依舊會被你占據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而且反過來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不讓你消失 她的靈魂就不會受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就在你出來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把你折磨得生不如死就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你對我重要的人下了手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你死得輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我會用盡一切手段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你生不如死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要讓你感受一切痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不會讓你解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你是敵人 但我絕對不會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 我會送你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙的氣息 好像已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,答案？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會跟著你來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以後是否還要繼續跟隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我對你提問的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 始 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 今後我也想繼續留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣只會讓你更痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,又不像希婭一樣 只要沒有月就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我也會想要獨占你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想讓你只注視著我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我會嫉妒月 也會感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有時也會覺得痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果現在退縮了 我肯定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我確信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說 最好的決定就是留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你覺得沒問題 那我也不會多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,始 剛剛的話想聽你再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,對 你說因為對什麼出手所以生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 再說一下有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是魔法陣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,難道我們攻略成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我沒想到這就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,總感覺比其他的迷宮要簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡已經足夠難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而且這個世界的人信仰肯定非常堅定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果讓他們見到了那些瘋狂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,的確也有可能這就結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,時間正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來不像是沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,香織小姐 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,受傷了嗎 回復魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有一半是我在撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 香織 難道說你已經能走路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其實從一開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 究竟發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快 說來聽聽 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,和香織幽會調情了嗎 調情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,久違的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是和始親了親而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰主動的 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是我主動的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,始為了我而生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點沒忍住 所以親上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 和我那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為你會夾著尾巴逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:16:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 始也叫我乾脆逃走算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我和月之間的差距 我早就看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 本來我就是看開了才跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是看到我們之間的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我有點忘了這回事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,直接放棄不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕了嗎 怕被我搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,少神氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了我在始的心裡也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我決定要繼續努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爭取成為他心中最特別的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不管別人怎麼說我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那我依舊接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 再生之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要依賴神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,做出你自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走出你自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,遵從自由之意志 才能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,攻略證明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,四個證明都湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就能挑戰樹海的大迷宮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是要強制驅逐我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,月 準備空間魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不死之身能溶解一切甚至還能掌控大海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這下該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我和月她們 雖然用火發起了攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,月和緹奧的炎屬性魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,目前算是不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,始 你想到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想在海裡用火只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,讓那個果凍再生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,趕在它生成之前消滅它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,運氣好的話應該能打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,始 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不過得花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,三分鐘 只要能撐過三分鐘就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它想把我們吞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,實在不行的話 就讓我化龍為盾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 時間還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,始兄 讓大叔來幫你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,裡兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是始兄的好朋友 裡兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是只要三分鐘就能對付那個大胃王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點搞不清狀況 總之多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,裡兄 這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 我正到處閒晃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,突然感覺到一股強大而熟悉的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就趕來看看發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那些魚 還有大胃王是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那些魚群 是我用能力誘導來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,至於大胃王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是自古以來盤踞在海裡的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是天災
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有時也被稱為魔物的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,給你吃個夠 撐死你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,會爆炸的話你提前說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 裡兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛老師進神山已經三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯塔教皇明明說了很快就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉也還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然跟陛下說了不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 妮亞小姐也不見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼接二連三的實在讓人不放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去問問那些護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也這麼覺得 不過找了半天都不見人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,梅爾德團長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我們在說小愛老師的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛我聽說是因為南雲的事去了神山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,去了之後一直沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,護衛的人也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,另外還有一些人也是突然就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其實 我們目前正在調查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,主人覺得不太合適
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你的學生們想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,才更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以待到時機成熟之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要暫時從主人的棋盤上退場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 新的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:06.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:12.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:18.06,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:24.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:29.90,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.66,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:35.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:41.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:47.38,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:53.09,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:58.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.77,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:07.11,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
